- Polenta.

347
00:14:07,291 --> 00:14:10,260
Potato cake. Their signature.

348
00:14:10,260 --> 00:14:12,261
Rice cake.

349
00:14:12,896 --> 00:14:13,997
Meatball.

350
00:14:13,997 --> 00:14:16,900
This'll fill you up.

351
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:18,669
This is basically a full meal.

352
00:14:18,669 --> 00:14:19,870
This is the appetizer.

353
00:14:19,870 --> 00:14:21,905
