360
00:14:43,694 --> 00:14:46,162
This won't be easy at all.

361
00:14:47,064 --> 00:14:48,699
I'm excited.

362
00:14:48,699 --> 00:14:51,068
A platter like this, see,

363
00:14:51,068 --> 00:14:54,404
- it's a simple dish you finish
