A pinch of salt.

369
00:15:06,416 --> 00:15:08,885
[All buttoned up]

370
00:15:08,885 --> 00:15:12,589
[Glued to the senior's side]

371
00:15:12,589 --> 00:15:15,532
[The rookie watches like a hawk]

372
00:15:15,532 --> 00:15:19,035
[Eyes wide open]

373
00:15:19,035 --> 00:15:21,365
