That's how you roll it all the way through.

397
00:16:14,284 --> 00:16:17,319
[Focus again]

398
00:16:17,319 --> 00:16:18,922
[Roll]

399
00:16:18,922 --> 00:16:20,857
Yes, that's how you do it.

400
00:16:20,857 --> 00:16:22,025
He rolls them well.

401
00:16:22,025 --> 00:16:25,095
- Good, nicely done.
- Perfect.

402
00:16:25,095 --> 00:16:27,030
Drink some coffee while it's hot.

403
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:28,765
