- Drink it now, then keep going.

404
00:16:28,765 --> 00:16:30,200
Okay.

405
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:32,469
So you can drink it hot,
and then we can continue.

406
00:16:32,469 --> 00:16:34,404
[On senior An's cue, down it goes]
Is it sour?

407
00:16:34,404 --> 00:16:35,540
[Slurp]

408
00:16:37,073 --> 00:16:40,877
[Caffeine, topped up]

409
00:16:40,877 --> 00:16:44,114
[Kwon picks up the pace]
So you prep all that ahead of time.

410
00:16:44,114 --> 00:16:46,716
Since orders keep rolling in.

411
00:16:46,716 --> 00:16:49,653
[A popular dish, so prepped in bulk ahead]

412
00:16:49,653 --> 00:16:52,027
[Beef rolls, finally ready to go]

413
00:16:52,027 --> 00:16:54,490
