416
00:16:59,262 --> 00:17:00,230
[Beef rolls already prepped, set aside]

417
00:17:00,230 --> 00:17:01,698
This foresta verde,

418
00:17:01,698 --> 00:17:04,134
[Oven items first]
- you have to put rice. - Rice.

419
00:17:04,134 --> 00:17:06,369
[Rice cake]
Two rice cakes.

420
00:17:06,369 --> 00:17:08,538
[Rice cake, beef roll, potato cake]
Two pieces of potato cake.

421
00:17:08,538 --> 00:17:11,508
- Four meatballs.
- Four.

422
00:17:11,508 --> 00:17:13,877
That's just one item on the menu.

423
00:17:13,877 --> 00:17:15,245
So much to do.

424
00:17:15,245 --> 00:17:17,481
[Olive oil, and...]
- Oil. - Oil.

425
00:17:17,481 --> 00:17:20,449
