428
00:17:28,992 --> 00:17:30,727
- Polenta.
- Okay.

429
00:17:30,727 --> 00:17:32,395
- So much to do.
- Okay.

430
00:17:32,395 --> 00:17:33,864
Oh, so that one needs frying now.

431
00:17:33,864 --> 00:17:35,198
The polenta.

432
00:17:35,198 --> 00:17:36,733
- Right.
- On the right. Okay.

433
00:17:36,733 --> 00:17:38,101
[Plop]

434
00:17:38,101 --> 00:17:40,303
[Mid-air drop]

435
00:17:40,303 --> 00:17:42,105
