438
00:17:46,025 --> 00:17:47,878
- Okay.
- Right.

439
00:17:47,878 --> 00:17:50,347
- Whoa, no joke.
- He's really kind.

440
00:17:50,347 --> 00:17:52,682
- He's kind.
- He's kind, isn't he?

441
00:17:52,682 --> 00:17:54,552
