So fun.

483
00:19:24,307 --> 00:19:27,744
You don't need to put it in the fridge, this.

484
00:19:27,744 --> 00:19:29,512
I'm telling you how,
but do it however it works for you.

485
00:19:29,512 --> 00:19:30,680
Yeah.

486
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:34,150
